imdb.plot outline: Actress, Model, Author and Philanthropist Christina Cooper produces her own televised talk show at 23 years old, making her the youngest woman to host and produce her own talk show in history. Tune in to her show to see who's inspiring people within the community and to also be inspired by amazing people, amazing stories, and amazing celebrities spreading inspiration around the country.
